name: Marines & Aliens Game
description:
Space Game is a 100% on-chain collectible based strategy game. All metadata and pixel sprites are generated and stored completely on-chain. No API and IPFS are used.

[Website](https://spacenft.game) | 
[Discord](http://discord.gg/spacegame) |
[Twitter](https://twitter.com/spacenftdotgame)

MAIN COLLECTION:

[Protoss](https://opensea.io/collection/spacegame-protoss) |
[MnAv2](https://opensea.io/collection/sgmarinesandaliensv2) | [Spidox](https://opensea.io/collection/sgspidoxdroid) | [Founder Crate](https://opensea.io/collection/sgfounderpass) 

EGG COLLECTION: 

[Water Egg](https://opensea.io/collection/sgwateregg) | [Fire Egg](https://opensea.io/collection/sgfireegg) | [Poison Egg](https://opensea.io/collection/sgpoisonegg) | [Darkness Egg](https://opensea.io/collection/sgdarknessegg)
